üí°Introducing PCOS : A Comprehensive Digital Platform for Managing PCOS

Polycystic Ovary Syndrome (PCOS) impacts millions of women globally, often making everyday health management overwhelming due to fragmented tools, lack of personalization, and limited access to professional support.

PCOS App is designed as an all-in-one mobile solution that combines advanced technology, medical guidance, and community support to empower women with PCOS to take control of their health in a smarter, more structured way.

Core Features of PCOS App:

‚úÖDetailed tracking of symptoms, including weight, glucose levels, mood changes, skin and hair health
Menstrual cycle monitoring with AI-assisted prediction of irregularities and symptom flare-ups
‚úÖCustomized dietary plans and fitness recommendations tailored for PCOS management
‚úÖSecure in-app telemedicine consultations with gynecologists, endocrinologists, and nutritionists
Stress management tools, guided meditation, CBT modules, and sleep tracking
‚úÖCommunity discussion forums and support groups for sharing experiences and wellness tips
‚úÖIntegration with wearable devices for real-time tracking of heart rate, physical activity, and sleep
Technology Stack

Front-end:

‚û°Ô∏èDeveloped using Android Studio (Java), ensuring a responsive, native mobile experience optimized for Android devices
Designed with a clean, intuitive interface for easy navigation and personalized dashboards
Backend

‚û°Ô∏èPowered by PHP, managing server-side operations, API integrations, and business logic
‚û°Ô∏èUtilizes SQL databases for secure, structured storage of user data, health records, and consultation logs
Security and Compliance

The platform prioritizes user privacy, following healthcare data protection regulations such as HIPAA and GDPR
Strong encryption and authentication mechanisms ensure secure handling of sensitive health information
What Sets PCOS Health Companion Apart

Combines AI-driven insights, medical expertise, and lifestyle guidance in a single app
Offers personalized, evidence-based recommendations rather than generic advice
Seamlessly connects users with certified healthcare professionals
Builds a supportive community environment focused on both physical and mental well-being
Our Mission
PCOS Health Companion is committed to transforming the way women manage PCOS by delivering a unified, smart, and accessible solution that blends technology, healthcare, and community.

